title: Duke University Chapel
author: NoahDavid2012
pages:
Duke University Chapel
is a chapel located in
the center of Duke
University in Durham,
North Carolina. It has
3 pipe organs, 1 with
5,003 and another with
6,900 pipes. It also
has a 50-bell carillon,
the heaviest bell
G-Natural is 11,200
pounds, while the
lightest is only 10.5
